properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 17 at 2:47PM AKST until January 19 at 6:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 4 to 8 inches.

* WHERE...Southern Inner Channels.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Saturday to 6 AM AKST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Snow will begin Saturday morning and could
begin accumulating quickly. Final snowfall amounts will be
contingent on a possible change to rain early Sunday morning.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM SATURDAY TO 6 AM AKST SUNDAY FOR THE SOUTHERN INNER CHANNELS
